# 🖼️ Image-to-Text AI Model (English + Marathi)

This project uses **Google Gemini API** to analyze accident scene images and generate meaningful text summaries in **English and Marathi**.  
It can describe accident scenes and provide short rescue instructions in simple language.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Accepts one or multiple image URLs.
- Describes accident scene in English.
- Translates output to Marathi automatically.
- Uses Gemini-2.5-Pro for multimodal image reasoning.

---

## 🧠 Tech Stack
- Python  
- Google Gemini API  
- Google Translate API  
- Pillow  
- dotenv for API key management  

---

